## Basic Usage

```yaml
{{.ConfigSection}}:
  {{.Name}}:
    source: OWNER/{{.BinaryName}}@v1
```

## With Configuration

```yaml
{{.ConfigSection}}:
  {{.Name}}:
    source: OWNER/{{.BinaryName}}@v1
    config:
      example_option: "value"
```

